method.name: CreateCompositesData
method.abstract: Create a default composites properties on the current material.

method.name: ExistCompositesData
method.abstract: Returns true if a composites properties exists on the current material.

method.name: CuredThickness
method.abstract: returns or set the cured thicknes defined in Composites tab in mm.

method.name: FabricWidth
method.abstract: returns or set the fabric width defined in Composites tab in mm.

method.name: LimitDeformation
method.abstract: returns or set the limit deformation defined in Composites tab in radian.

method.name: MassCost
method.abstract: returns or set the cost per mess defined in Composites tab in $ per kg.

method.name: MaterialType
method.abstract: returns or set the material type defined in Composites tab.

method.name: MaxDeformation
method.abstract: returns or set the maximum deformation defined in Composites tab in radian.

method.name: SurfacicWeigth
method.abstract: returns or set the surfacic weigth defined in Composites tab in kg per m2.

method.name: UncuredThickness
method.abstract: returns or set the uncured thicknes defined in Composites tab in mm.
